description:
At the ACT Bootcamp, you can get prepped for the ACT in as little as one weekend.

Our Harvard student tutors cover all of the material on the exam, providing the most concise and effective coverage of ACT concepts. available on the Internet.

Watch a short lecture and take a follow up quiz to test and engrain your knowledge. You can test your knowledge at the end of the course with a full length practice test.

We aced our tests, now let us help you ace yours.
title: Harvard ACT Test Prep Bootcamp
